"entities\": [{\"begin\": 301, \"end\": 312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greco-Roman_wrestling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.933090402297723e-41, \"text\": \"Greco-Roman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greco-Roman_wrestling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greco-Roman_wrestling\"}, {\"begin\": 329, \"end\": 332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"score\": 0.9960495115118523, \"rank\": 0.0039587367316469115, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\"}, {\"begin\": 333, \"end\": 336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\", \"score\": 0.9952175613418781, \"rank\": 0.0048052724058042185, \"text\": \"Rau\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\"}, {\"begin\": 425, \"end\": 429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999993103344982, \"rank\": 6.896611240163891e-07, \"text\": \"Iran\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That pitted Rau against Kyrgyzstan's Uzur Dzhuzupbekov.\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 518, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 475, \"end\": 478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\", \"score\": 0.9952175613418781, \"rank\": 0.0048052724058042185, \"text\": \"Rau\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\"}, {\"begin\": 487, \"end\": 497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyrgyzstan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9589176960164512, \"rank\": 0.04284229268685822, \"text\": \"Kyrgyzstan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyrgyzstan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyrgyzstan_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rau appeared to take the lead early in the contest; however, a potential takedown was called a \\\"slip-throw\\\" by the on-mat official.\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 651, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 520, \"end\": 523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\", \"score\": 0.9952175613418781, \"rank\": 0.0048052724058042185, \"text\": \"Rau\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shortly after that call, Rau was hit for passivity.\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 677, \"end\": 680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\", \"score\": 0.9952175613418781, \"rank\": 0.0048052724058042185, \"text\": \"Rau\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to the point for the passive call, Dzhuzupbekov was able to capitalize on the ensuing par terre restart and used a high gut to turn Rau for four points and a huge 5-0 lead.\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 888, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The second period began and the official hit Dzhuzpbekov for passivity and gave Rau the chance to work from par terre.\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 1008, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 970, \"end\": 973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\", \"score\": 0.9952175613418781, \"rank\": 0.0048052724058042185, \"text\": \"Rau\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Rau was looking to work from a head pinch, the official determined that Dzhuzupbekov committed a foul which made the score 5-3.\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1012, \"end\": 1015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\", \"score\": 0.9952175613418781, \"rank\": 0.0048052724058042185, \"text\": \"Rau\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Late in the period, Rau was able to earn another point via step out to pull within one point.\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1161, \"end\": 1164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\", \"score\": 0.9952175613418781, \"rank\": 0.0048052724058042185, \"text\": \"Rau\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As he was pushing for a potential score, Dzhuzupbekov got a throw of his own for four points and that sequence clinched a 9-4 victory - ending Rau's tournament.\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1395, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1378, \"end\": 1381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\", \"score\": 0.9952175613418781, \"rank\": 0.0048052724058042185, \"text\": \"Rau\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"2022 World Champion Dom Parrish was next to take the mat and she had the toughest possible first-round opponent in the women's 53 kg freestyle bracket, Akari Fujinami of Japan.\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1549, \"end\": 1563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akari_Fujinami\", \"score\": 0.99999955781969, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Akari Fujinami\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akari_Fujinami\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akari_Fujinami\"}, {\"begin\": 1567, \"end\": 1572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_baseball_team\", \"score\": 0.9988265275007927, \"rank\": 0.0008525901558989584, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_baseball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_baseball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fujinami is a two-time world champion who won her most recent title without surrendering a point.\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1671, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1574, \"end\": 1582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_destroyer_Fujinami\", \"score\": 0.9999999999708962, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fujinami\", \"types\": [\"Q11446\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_destroyer_Fujinami\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_destroyer_Fujinami\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The match began favorably for Parrish who was able to fend off the initial offensive surge from Fujinami.\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1778, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1703, \"end\": 1710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maxfield_Parrish\", \"score\": 0.9999999999745341, \"rank\": 2.528700283826941e-11, \"text\": \"Parrish\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maxfield_Parrish\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maxfield_Parrish\"}, {\"begin\": 1769, \"end\": 1777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_destroyer_Fujinami\", \"score\": 0.9999999999708962, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fujinami\", \"types\": [\"Q11446\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_destroyer_Fujinami\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_destroyer_Fujinami\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, she wasn't able to stop a low leg attack for a takedown and a 2-0 lead for the Japanese star.\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1873, \"end\": 1881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.8475903444282004, \"rank\": 0.0933667230675966, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"